{"tid":2219092,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台藝人出席央視國慶晚會合唱《我的祖國》 台陸委會：不應協助統戰宣傳","createTime":"2020-09-26T15:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T20:06:28.000Z","uid":49776,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8055fcce30c00c8402244061e29245b629022ebb","tid":2219092,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"大陸央視今日（26 日）在微博公布 9 月 30 日的「中國夢‧祖國頌」國慶晚會表演名單，台灣藝人歐陽娜娜會與香港、中國藝人合唱開場曲「我的祖國」；張韶涵會與其他大陸藝人合唱抗疫宣傳歌曲「守護」。台灣的大陸委員會今日回覆多間當地傳媒查詢，強調國民不應支持、協助中共對台進行統戰宣傳，傷害中華民國的國家認同，並表示將密切關注相關情況，倘有涉及違反兩岸條例相關規定，將依法查處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/WhatsApp20Image202020-09-2620at2010.11.0020PM_xQgaC_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FWhatsApp20Image202020-09-2620at2010.11.0020PM_xQgaC_1200x0.jpeg&h=636caf5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%B0%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E5%9C%8B%E6%85%B6%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%83-%E5%90%88%E5%94%B1-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%A5%96%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3%E6%AD%8C-%E5%8F%B0%E9%99%B8%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0%E5%AE%A3%E5%82%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E8%2597%259D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2585%25B6%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%2594%25B1-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%25AD%258C-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%2599%25B8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%2582%25B3%2F&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0nr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=7bc52029\" data-ef-url=\"https://embe