恢復國民黨籍（其他包括新黨議員秦儷舫回鍋國民黨等）；後歐陽龍獲中國國民黨提名在大安、文山選區競選連任市議員成功三次。有趣的是，初次以無黨當選的歐陽龍，也參與新黨議員研習營[1]。2018年九合一大選落選，終結連任[2]。<br />\n<br />\n2019年1月2日，國民黨中常會通過，由台北市前議員歐陽龍接任文傳會副主委兼發言人[3]。<br />\n<br />\n佢老豆都唔係啲咩好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085386b7bf9c1d0c3672dfbfbd243adaabf5c949","tid":2219092,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"香港少數民族代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1464212c60a371c0e39ed3b98d1973f2041a8f8","tid":2219092,"uid":369040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:40:15.000Z","msg":"如果返去50年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3626dbc5f55ae913e41e3438727f35b0f181f921","tid":2219092,"uid":263223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"唱得我的祖國即係認自己係支國人喇，仲唔轉國籍換護照？"},{"pid":"1de0915b690627907c29d2f402905ba54b9ee10b","tid":2219092,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"歐陽娜娜支那人黎架，台灣個個都屌佢"},{"pid":"456fdf76b0b91f141b3022d6db93c90951b5961d","tid":2219092,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"唔見晒香港啲護旗手<br />\n係咪知道無論你點表忠都搵唔到食<br />\n又要死返黎香港乞<br />\n好似譚伯同hsbc咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d298d30e64703a67def927dc4798d43879d2f496","tid":2219092,"uid":36182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T17:00:47.000Z","msg":"去完唔洗番台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a2c5b39bb13be680fa70839e3011e8fb05fbe8e","tid":2219092,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"